elements.body: Start the simulation by right clicking on the "Mission Simulation" SimulationConfig, and selecting "Simulation -> Run"
Here, a data frame is assumed to have size 1024 bytes, and takes anywhere from 0.5s to 2.5s to be sent to its destination (this is meant to account for connection lags, resends, etc.)
